{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58bf172e92","title":"关于接管的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4364ca6a79","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"58bf172e92"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"11239c6a44","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"谢富治，当时任公安部部长、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3d96d5c76e","type":"title","text":"关于接管的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92"},{"id":"11239c6a44","type":"paragraph","text":"接管是不可避免的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92"},{"id":"8a64bfa351","type":"paragraph","text":"我们这个政府，过去是上面派去少数干部和下面大多数留用人员组成了政府，不是工人、农民起来闹革命夺得了政府，这就很容易产生封建主义、修正主义的东西。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92"},{"id":"c40915700c","type":"paragraph","text":"谢富治叫：我们老一点的同志，对这个运动不理解，从开始就不理解，到现在还不理解，转不过弯来。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92"},{"id":"9e3892dbd5","type":"paragraph","text":"转不过弯来靠边站，但给饭吃。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92"},{"id":"ee24267360","type":"paragraph","text":"谢富治：昨天向主席谈到，联合行动委员会有许多高千子弟。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92"},{"id":"b582b8cb6c","type":"paragraph","text":"这是阶级斗争。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92"}],"page":{"id":"5a0ca4d092","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"58bf172e92","start":300,"end":300}}}},"__N_SSG":true}